== Events == * [[Ōtoku]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1087]] {{ill|January 3|ja|1月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – In this year, Emperor [[Hakuba Tennō|白河天皇]] abdicated in favor of his young successor, who then began his reign as an incumbent emperor while serving as a retired emperor (上皇) during the subsequent period of cloistered rule. * [[Chishō]] 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1180]] {{ill|December 14|ja|12月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Taira no Kiyomori returned the capital from Fukuhara to Heian-kyō. * [[Shōgen (Japan)|Shōgen]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1260]] {{ill|January 9|ja|1月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Emperor Go-Fukakusa was forced by his father, former Emperor Go-Saga, to cede the throne to his younger brother, leading to a split in the imperial line between the Daikakuji and Jōmyōin houses. * {{ill|Bunroku|ja|文禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1594]] {{ill|January 17|ja|1月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – By imperial command, the printed edition of the "Kobun-kōkyō" (an edict of Keichō) was produced; this marked the production of Japan’s first wooden movable type printed book. == Births == * [[An'ei]] 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1780]] {{ill|December 21|ja|12月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kurozumi Sōchū|ja|黒住宗忠|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the founder of the Kurozumi school of Confucian thought (died [[1850]]). * [[Tenmei]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1785]] {{ill|January 6|ja|1月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ashiro Hirokun|ja|足代弘訓|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a Kokugaku scholar (died [[1856]]). == Deaths == * [[Kōji (Muromachi period)|Kōji]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1556]] {{ill|January 7|ja|1月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Oda Nobuhiro|ja|織田信光|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander (born [[1516]]).
