* [[Tenmei]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1785]] {{ill|January 6|ja|1月6日}}) – {{ill|Ashiro Hirokun|ja|足代弘訓}}, a Kokugaku scholar (died [[1856]]).
